    <p class="muted" style="max-width: 46rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">
      The Lisbon edition carried over much of the deferred 2020 programme. It ran across two days,
      built around parallel panels, two keynote addresses, and a closing multidisciplinary
      roundtable. The session list below is reconstructed from the published programme.
    </p>

